trans-unit.source: Represents the resolution supported by a printer.
trans-unit.target: Representa a resolução suportada por uma impressora.

trans-unit.source: This class is used by the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties to get the printer resolutions that are available on the printer and to set the printing resolution for a page, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe é usada pelo <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>e <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Propriedades para obter as resoluções de impressora que estão disponíveis na impressora e definir a resolução da impressão de uma página, respectivamente.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> property to determine whether the printer resolution type is the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> value <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.
trans-unit.target: Use a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>propriedade para determinar se o tipo de resolução de impressora é o <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>valor <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>

trans-unit.source: If so, use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> properties to determine the printer resolution in the horizontal and vertical directions, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Nesse caso, use o <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A>e <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A>Propriedades para determinar a resolução da impressora nas direções horizontais e verticais, respectivamente.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information on printing, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace overview.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre como imprimir, consulte o <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>Visão geral do namespace.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.target: Obtém a resolução horizontal de impressora, em pontos por polegada.

trans-unit.source: `dmPrintQuality` is a member of the `DEVMODE` (device mode) structure, which defines constants that map to printer quality settings.
trans-unit.target: `dmPrintQuality`é um membro do `DEVMODE` estrutura (modo de dispositivo), que define as constantes que são mapeados para as configurações de qualidade de impressora.

trans-unit.source: The X property contains the value `DMRES_HIGH` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_MEDIUM` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_LOW` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, and `DMRES_DRAFT` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade X contém o valor `DMRES_HIGH` se <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>for definido como <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_MEDIUM` se <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>for definido como <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_LOW` se <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>for definido como <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, e `DMRES_DRAFT` se <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>é definida como <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>
